Katari - dropdown menu

 This is a javascript based drop down menu for Katari. This module provides a
 weblet to render the menu.

 There are two types of menu in this module: a menubar menu, that is a standard
 horizontal bar with all the top level menu entries, and a popup, content-like
 menu, that occupies much less space, a button that when clicked displays the
 top level menu entries.

 If you want to add a drop down menu to your application, use:

-----
  <@katari.weblet "dropdown-menu" "menu" "bar"/>
-----

 or

-----
  <@katari.weblet "dropdown-menu" "menu" "context"/>
-----

 to show the menu bar or context menu style respectively.

